=============================
pathurl: object-oriented URLs
=============================

.. image:: https://github.com/spapanik/pathurl/actions/workflows/build.yml/badge.svg
  :alt: Build
  :target: https://github.com/spapanik/pathurl/actions/workflows/build.yml
